purpose.example:
       Some product attributes:



		fuel flow rate;



		required speed;



		operating temperature;



		physical shape;



		dimensional tolerance.

	Some interactions: 



		physical interaction, such as two mechanical gears meshing;



		optical interaction, such as an infrared connection between a
         remote control and a television; 



		electrical interaction, such as the current at 240 volts,
50 hertz from a domestic supply as required by a refrigerator.

